ir kindness. We are looking forward to see you at the wedding." style="transform:none" data-framer-component-type="RichTextContainer"><p style="--font-selector:R0Y7WWFsZGV2aS1yZWd1bGFy;--framer-font-family:&quot;Yaldevi&quot;, &quot;Yaldevi Placeholder&quot;, sans-serif;--framer-font-size:20px;--framer-text-alignment:center;--framer-text-color:rgb(105, 107, 54)" class="framer-text">To help you feel at ease and enjoy every moment of the celebrations, we’ve gathered a few thoughtful details we’d love for you to know before the big day.</p></div></div><div class="framer-1q28ybr" data-framer-name="Information"><div class="framer-1wq5nfy-container" data-framer-name="Hashtag" name="Hashtag"><!--$--><div name="Hashtag" class="framer-5gCIX framer-1ar8i4h framer-v-1ar8i4h" data-framer-name="Desktop" style="height: 100%; width: 100%; opacity: 1;"><div class="framer-1x8nr7w" style="opacity: 1;"><div class="framer-f4gc8b" style="opacity: 1;"><div class="framer-1jzdh0c" data-framer-name="ChatGPT Image Aug 20, 2025 at 02_43_47 PM 1" style="opacity: 1;"><div style="position:absolute;border-radius:inherit;corner-shape:inherit;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;left:0" data-framer-background-image-wrapper="true"><img decoding="auto" width="171" height="177" src="./City5_files/5y8vl5sZQRnq3EHTA5uUoYOFwI.png" alt="" style="display:block;width:100%;height:100%;border-radius:inherit;corner-shape:inherit;object-position:center;object-fit:contain"></div></div></div><div class="framer-v0c8nb" data-framer-name="Hashtag" style="--extracted-r6o4lv: rgb(105, 107, 54); --framer-paragraph-spacing: 0px; transform: none; opacity: 1;" data-framer-component-type="RichTextContainer"><p style="--font-selector:R0Y7QWJvcmV0by1yZWd1bGFy;--framer-font-family:&quot;Aboreto&quot;, sans-serif;--framer-font-size:32px;--framer-text-alignment:center;--framer-text-color:var(--extracted-r6o4lv, rgb(105, 107, 54))" class="framer-text">Hashtag</p></div><div class="framer-1ilsgfh" data-framer-name="#BadriKiDulhania" style="--ex